N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 330.3 - Notification to applicant of disapproval

State Regulations

Upon refusal to recommend approval of an application for
authority to practice, the Psychology Practice Committee shall notify the
applicant, in writing, of such refusal. Notes
